# AI Funding Radar Environment Variables

## Required
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-your-key-here

## Qdrant Configuration
QDRANT_URL=http://localhost:6333

## Google Sheets Configuration (Optional - for demo, can use without)
NEXT_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_SHEET_ID=your-sheet-id
GOOGLE_PROJECT_ID=your-project-id
GOOGLE_PRIVATE_KEY_ID=your-key-id
GOOGLE_PRIVATE_KEY="-----BEGIN PRIVATE KEY-----\n...\n-----END PRIVATE KEY-----\n"
GOOGLE_SHEETS_CLIENT_EMAIL=your-email@your-project.iam.gserviceaccount.com
GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your-client-id
